### Get All Vouchers (Public — customer browsing)
GET http://localhost:5001/api/v1/promotions?page=1&limit=10

### Get All Vouchers (Public — filter by store)
GET http://localhost:5001/api/v1/promotions?storeId=fd102949-677b-4843-ada1-8a940c738438

### Get All Vouchers (Public — filter by discount type)
GET http://localhost:5001/api/v1/promotions?discountType=PERCENT

### Get Available Vouchers (Public — checkout filtering)
GET http://localhost:5001/api/v1/promotions/available?storeId=fd102949-677b-4843-ada1-8a940c738438&orderAmount=100000

### List Vouchers (Internal — admin panel with filters)
GET http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/vouchers?page=1&limit=20&storeId=fd102949-677b-4843-ada1-8a940c738438&isActive=true&discountType=PERCENT
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Create Voucher (Internal)
POST http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/vouchers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "code": "KM_MOI_2024",
  "discountType": "PERCENT",
  "discountValue": 10,
  "maxUsage": 100,
  "minOrderAmount": 50000,
  "maxDiscount": 20000,
  "isActive": true
}

### Create Voucher (Internal — store-specific)
POST http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/vouchers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "code": "STORE10",
  "discountType": "PERCENT",
  "discountValue": 10,
  "storeId": "fd102949-677b-4843-ada1-8a940c738438",
  "expiresAt": "2026-12-31T23:59:59.000Z"
}

### Update Voucher (Internal)
PATCH http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/vouchers/voucher-uuid-here
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "discountValue": 15,
  "isActive": false
}

### Delete Voucher (Internal)
DELETE http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/vouchers/voucher-uuid-here
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
